"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-9cX","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":32272,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/18\/abu-dharr-loves-allah-rasul\/","url_meta":{"origin":35399,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Abu Dharr loves Allah and His Messenger","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Dharr reported: He said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, a man loves a people, but he cannot do good deeds like they do.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou, O Abu Dharr, will be with those you love.\u201d Abu Dharr said, \u201cI love Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13890,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/02\/may-allah-love-you-too\/","url_meta":{"origin":35399,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Brotherhood: May Allah, for whom you love me, love you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 2, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man was with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, when another man passed by and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I love this man.\u201d The Prophet asked, \u201cHave you told him?\u201d He said no. The Prophet said, \u201cTell him.\u201d So he went\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15433,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/greet-salaam-again-again\/","url_meta":{"origin":35399,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Greet with peace again and again","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen one of you meets his brother, let him greet him with peace. If they are separated by a tree, a wall, or a stone, and he meets him again, let him greet him with peace\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3163,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/10\/be-just-with-children\/","url_meta":{"origin":35399,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Justice: Parents must be fair with their children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cBe just between your children. Be just between your children.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3544 Grade:\u00a0Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064f\u0651\u0639\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u064e\u0634\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0639\u0652\u062f\u0650\u0644\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0627\u062f\u0650\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1931,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/02\/05\/criticize-no-naming-shaming\/","url_meta":{"origin":35399,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Refutation: The Prophet criticizes without shaming","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported:\u00a0If the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, heard something bad about a man, he would not name him by saying, \u201cWhat is the matter with this person that he says this?\u201d Rather, the Prophet would say, \u201cWhat is the matter with some people who say this?\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13739,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/25\/security-asks-bismillah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35399,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Security: Grant refuge to whoever asks by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever seeks refuge with you in the name of Allah, grant him refuge. Whoever asks you in the name of Allah, give it to him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 5109 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u06